		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Winter solstice</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the astronomical and cultural event of winter solstice, also known as midwinter. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Winter_solstice_(disambiguation)" title="Winter solstice (disambiguation)">Winter solstice (disambiguation)</a>, <a href="/wiki/Midwinter_(disambiguation)" title="Midwinter (disambiguation)">Midwinter (disambiguation)</a> or also see <a href="/wiki/Solstice" title="Solstice">Solstice</a>.</div>
